    - m_Type: 0
      Title:
        m_Untranslated: Rotation Not Quite Right
      Text:
        m_Untranslated: "We want the shield to rotate around the center of the player,
          not around its own center. We could adjust the code to use the RotateAround
          function (which takes an added pivot point location as a parameter) instead
          of Rotate however, this would make our Rotate script only useful for the
          shield, not for other things we might want to rotate which do have correct
          pivots. \r\nInstead, we can leverage the power of the Game Hierarchy to
          rotate the shield around the player center. \r\n"
