    - m_Type: 0
      Title:
        m_Untranslated: 
      Text:
        m_Untranslated: "Run the game and see what happens to the shield as the player
          rotates.\nNotice how the shield also rotates, but around the center point
          of the player (i.e. the pivot point of the shield\u2019s parent). We could
          add the Rotate script to the Player, however this would make the player
          constantly rotate (instead of responding to user input), and keep the shield
          always at the front of the ship (we want the shield to rotate independently
          of the player in this version)."
